        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "It's a very rare pill, and it should only be taken by #p407#, and no one else. If you have any desire to take that pill for yourself, don't even think about it. It will only work on #p407#."
